            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x67a,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... How to get stronger... Training..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x67b,
            "msg_string": "Plachta wants to get stronger... But there's no point in training with a doll's body..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x67c,
            "msg_string": "Oh... I know..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x67d,
            "msg_string": "If there's no point to exercise... Then maybe I can rebuild her body itself?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x67e,
            "msg_string": "I could use alchemy to Synthesize parts of Plachta with other items, and rebuild them..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x67f,
            "msg_string": "Obviously I wouldn't remake the whole thing, but this would definitely make her stronger!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x680,
            "msg_string": "Alright, I should talk to Plachta about this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x681,
            "msg_string": "You'll Synthesize items to rebuild my body... You've thought of something daring yet again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x682,
            "msg_string": "Ahaha... What do you think?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x683,
            "msg_string": "Well... To be honest, I have no idea how it will turn out..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x684,
            "msg_string": "But there should be potential. At the very least, it's far better than doing nothing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x685,
            "msg_string": "Then..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x686,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Let's try it, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x687,
            "msg_string": "Okay! Alright then, let's get started!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2288,
            "msg_string": "Please let me know when you're prepared."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can now use \"Doll Making\"!"
